Author: clittaryhilton
Text: i feel like you've read everything i've been thinking, its almost relieving being able to see these thoughts that i couldnt articulate

Author: ciruelax
Text: hey, I understand exactly what you mean and I’m so sorry you are feeling this way. I hate that my life revolves around my appearance and food and that it’s affecting me in so many ways. If you ever need someone to talk to, I’m here. I will be fasting with you, big hugs and take care.
